subject: Hello,
body:
Hello,
 My name is David Roche. I work with one of the prime banks in London, England, my retirement from the sector is very close and I wish to retire with something. I have a business proposal which I'd like to share with you if you are interested to hear it.
Reply to me and I will explain why I contacted you through this medium.
Thanks
Best regards,
David Roche.

subject: Re: Hello,
body:
Dear David Roche,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I am intrigued by your proposal and would like to hear more about it. Please provide more details so that I can better understand what you are proposing.

Best wishes,
Joanne
